Mobile Insurance Recent Activity Component
Show your mobile Policyholder site users a snapshot of the recent activity on their policies with the Mobile Insurance Recent Activity component.

This component is composed of a FlexCard and the LWC compiled from the FlexCard:

FlexCard: insRecentActivityContainerMobile_nds
LWC: cfInsRecentActivityContainerMobile_nds

Label: Insurance Recent Activity Container Mobile Newport

This component is designed for mobile. Looking for the Insurance Recent Activity component designed for desktop? Read Insurance Recent Activity Component.

The parts of this component are:

A text label:
Recent Activity
Recent activity displayed in a child component.
Read about the Mobile Recent Activity Child component hereMobile Insurance Recent Activity Child Component.

FlexCard Structure

This FlexCard is a container component that displays the child FlexCard (insRecentActivityChildMobile_nds) below a text element for the Recent Activity label.

You can add, remove, and change any of these elements based on what you want your users to see. To learn how see Add Elements to a FlexCard.

Many of the elements of this card contain Custom CSS styles. You can make changes to these styles to create a different look and feel. To learn how to work with Custom CSS in FlexCards, see Apply Custom CSS to a FlexCard Element .

Mobile Insurance Recent Activity Child Component
Show your mobile Policyholder site users a snapshot of their recent activity with the Mobile Insurance Recent Activity Child component. It's a child component that sits inside of the Mobile Insurance Recent Activity container component.

Customize this Component

To learn about how to customize this kind of component, see the Digital Experience Site Component Customization Overview
